The paper deals with the development of safe robots that can understand human values and intentions, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of natural language commands and the training of a critic to predict human responses involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also discusses the importance of human-robot interaction and the need for robots to align with human values, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
